text: "Cupid" is a 1961 song by Sam Cooke. It was released on 17 May, 1961 through RCA Records and went to number 17 in the United States and number 7 in the United Kingdom. The Johnny Nash version went to number 39 in the United States and number 19 in Ireland and The Spinners version went to number 4 in the United States and the United Kingdom and number 11 in Ireland.
